1.title: Adding two numbers
1.text: Double click on '+' to add the two numbers

1.title: Dividing two numbers
1.text: Double click on '-' to divide 1 with 2

1.title: Simplifying expression
1.text: Drag and smoosh to simplify the expression

2.title: Swapping terms in expression
2.text: Click and drag '+' to the far left side

2.title: Commuting & Joining
2.text: Commute the 3 to the far-left of the sum.

3.title: Factoring
3.text: Move one 'x' on top of another 'x' to factor

3.title: Distribution
3.text: Move the x into the sum to distribute
